&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text z-plain&quot;&gt;   }
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text z-plain&quot;&gt;   &#x2F;&#x2F; You can override the default device for e.g. keyboards by adding the device name to the last param
